                        <m id="6474">váthth</m>
                        <m id="1369">êen'nik</m>
                    </w>.
		</kar>
                <eng>Then after Grizzly Bear was already up the hill, again the <em>Ikxareyavs</em> did it, Buzzard and Hookbill had a fight.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar> 
		  "<w>
                        <m id="1656">iim</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6675">vúra</m>
                    </w>
                    <w><m id="1670">îin</m></w>
                    <w gl="you will not kill me"><m id="5082">pu</m><m id="4294">n</m><m id="3580"
                            >êek<sup>y</sup>ár</m><m id="1379">eesh</m><m id="1371">ara</m></w>?" <w><!-- accent should probably be the second one according to WB (although somewhat unclear), but JPH writes both; possibly because really iyk not iik? ?-->
                        <m id="792">atipimámvaan</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="126">achvúun</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="he told him"><m id="6175">ú</m><m id="2733">peer</m><m id="1369"
                        >anik</m></w>. </kar>
                <eng>"You are not going to kill me?" said Buzzard to Hookbill.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6847">xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="126">achvúun</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="he said">
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="4823">ppiip</m>
                    </w>: "<w><m id="4299">naa</m></w>
                    <w><m id="1670">îin</m></w>
                    <w gl="I shall not kill you"><m id="5082">pu</m><m id="3845">kin</m><m id="3580"
                            >îik<sup>y</sup>ár</m><m id="1379">eesh</m><m id="1371">ara</m></w>,<!-- accent should probably be the second one according to WB (although somewhat unclear), but JPH writes both-->
		    <w>
                        <m id="6383">vaa</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6675">vúra</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="4715">páy</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3922">k<sup>y</sup>ôomahich</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="I shall do to you">
                        <m id="4370">nu</m>
                        <m id="2657">níshsh</m>
                        <m id="1379">eesh</m>
                    </w>."
		  </kar>
                <eng>Then Hookbill said: "I am not going to kill you, This is all that I'm going to do to you."</eng>
            </s>
	    <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6847">xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="he picked him up">
                        <m id="6175">u</m>
                        <m id="1225">'êechip</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6847">xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="in the fireplace">
                        <m id="197">ahíram</m>
                        <m id="232">ak</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="he held it in the fire">
                        <m id="6175">ú</m>
                        <m id="3616">yuunkuri</m><!-- into water directional used instead of into fire-->
                    </w>
                    <w gl="his head">
                        <m id="4407">pa</m>
                        <m id="4260">mu</m>
                        <m id="969">xváa</m>
                    </w>,
		    <w>
