                    </w>
                    <w><m id="6881">xáy faat</m></w><!-- written as two words in published version-->
                    <w><m id="1729">ík</m></w>
                    <w><m id="4385">ôok</m></w>
                    <w gl="you come around again">
                        <m id="1418">i</m>
                        <m id="4469">páfyuk</m></w>,
			<w>
                        <m id="1656">iim</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="3752">k<sup>y</sup>áru</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6675">vura</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="not here">
                        <m id="5082">pu</m>
                        <m id="4385">'ôok</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="you will not stay">
                        <m id="1974">ikr</m>
                        <m id="1379">êevish</m>
                        <m id="1371">ara</m>
                    </w>," <w>
                        <m id="126">achvúun</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="they told him">
                        <m id="3977">kun</m>
                        <m id="2733">íppéer</m>
                    </w>.
		</kar>
                <eng>And they told him: "You yourself must not come around here, you too are not going to stay here," they told Hookbill.</eng>
            </s>
            <s>
                <kar>
                    <w>
                        <m id="6847">xás</m>
                    </w>
                    <w>
                        <m id="126">achvúun</m>
                    </w>
