                        <m id="1379">eesh</m>
                    </w>
                    <w gl="my song">
                        <m id="4326">nani</m>
                        <m id="4509">pákkuri</m>
                    </w>
                    <w><m id="6734">xáat</m></w>
                    <w><m id="4299">naa</m></w>
                    <w gl="not here">
                        <m id="5082">pu</m>
                        <m id="4385">'ôok</m>
                        <m id="1371">hara</m>
                    </w>." </kar>
                <eng>Then Hookbill said: "They will be singing my song, no matter if I am not
                    here."</eng>
            </s>
